{"id":245829,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-台风暴雨中上海民众坚持到市政府请愿抗/","date":"2012-08-08T22:00:59Z","modified":"2012-08-08T22:00:59Z","title":"维权网 | 台风暴雨中上海民众坚持到市政府请愿抗议（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>星期三，上海刮起台风，下着倾盆大雨。虽然　如此，仍然阻挡不了上海维权者们坚持到位于人民大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>号的上海市政府信访办抗议，抗议的民众主要是因为被贪官污吏掠夺农民土地，工人失业、暴力拆迁、司法不公、医疗纠纷等权利受到侵害，多年上访无果。上不起学、看不起病、无家可归，还遭受暴打，拘留，劳教，关黑监狱，送精神病院等迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>尽管在权大于法的专制制度下，“民告官”的案子法院常常是不立案，也不裁定。既使立案，也很难得到公正判决。但是上海的维权者们已经觉醒，纷纷拿起法律的武器捍卫自己被侵犯的权利，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>值得庆幸的是：越来越多的民众开始懂得，推动社会法治进步要靠大家的努力。在上海有一个为民众争取诉权的冯正虎被非法关押失去人身自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>个多月，却无法阻止上海民众维权的脚步。关押一个冯正虎，千万个“冯正虎”站起来，不管面临什么打压，上海的民众坚持每个星期一下午在市人大常委会集体请愿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>烈士遗孤胡琴珍的农村宅基地私房被强迫交易，导致胡琴珍得不到父母的补充安置份额而走上诉讼、举报、控告之路。胡琴珍不怕被抓、被关、被打击报复。今天在市信访办给维权者们分发《上海市民代表第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">59</span><span>次集访人大维护公民诉权》和《上海市民代表第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>次集访人大维护公民诉权》的信息资料，鼓励维权者们参与“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动。维权者们拿到了信息资料立刻仔仔细细地阅读起来，更增加了继续维权的决心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tx0ZSqsKZYo/UCKLZH6fxHI/AAAAAAAALFw/ku4NFIxkLZc/s1600/DSCI0862.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tx0ZSqsKZYo/UCKLZH6fxHI/AAAAAAAALFw/ku4NFIxkLZc/s320/DSCI0862.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z6mdcOZavlw/UCKLcuEyHII/AAAAAAAALF4/Evq5UofONXs/s1600/DSCI0863.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z6mdcOZavlw/UCKLcuEyHII/AAAAAAAALF4/Evq5UofONXs/s320/DSCI0863.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-o82gUJy_1KY/UCKLgtmxrSI/AAAAAAAALGA/qo3XQN7XWYM/s1600/DSCI0864.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-o82gUJy_1KY/UCKLgtmxrSI/AAAAAAAALGA/qo3XQN7XWYM/s320/DSCI0864.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-njxg8Isa-IU/UCKLkVcBLWI/AAAAAAAALGI/2chzf_3nvNU/s1600/DSCI0865.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-njxg8Isa-IU/UCKLkVcBLWI/AAAAAAAALGI/2chzf_3nvNU/s320/DSCI0865.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GDRjXaDh6kQ/UCKLouKD1lI/AAAAAAAALGQ/amtFcrOGeAs/s1600/DSCI0866.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GDRjXaDh6kQ/UCKLouKD1lI/AAAAAAAALGQ/amtFcrOGeAs/s320/DSCI0866.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SDhQfz8pivQ/UCKLuyC_RII/AAAAAAAALGY/6IdL9ya1Epg/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%AC%AC59%E6%AC%A1%E9%9B%86%E8%AE%BF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%AF%89%E6%9D%83.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SDhQfz8pivQ/UCKLuyC_RII/AAAAAAAALGY/6IdL9ya1Epg/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%AC%AC59%E6%AC%A1%E9%9B%86%E8%AE%BF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%AF%89%E6%9D%83.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>上海市民代表第59次集访人大维护公民诉权</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5WWxpgp6ZJg/UCKL3GiJo3I/AAAAAAAALGg/3nj7HAOQbv8/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%